<h2 id="comparisons">🔄 How Triple Whale Compares</h2>

We've tested Triple Whale against Northbeam, Rockerbox, and Hyros extensively. Here's where each tool wins:

**Triple Whale vs. Northbeam:** Northbeam offers more sophisticated multi-touch attribution models and better handles complex customer journeys with longer consideration periods. Triple Whale wins on ease of use, faster setup, and better Shopify-native features. For DTC brands under $10M with straightforward acquisition funnels, Triple Whale provides 90% of the value at 60% of the price.

**Triple Whale vs. Hyros:** Hyros excels for info-product and coaching businesses with phone sales and high-ticket items. Triple Whale dominates for traditional ecommerce with Shopify checkout. Different tools for different business models.

**Triple Whale vs. native platform pixels:** This isn't close. Triple Whale's first-party data approach captures 15-30% more conversions across iOS traffic. The unified view alone saves hours weekly. Any DTC brand spending over $30K monthly on paid media recaptures the subscription cost within the first month through better optimization decisions.

